<br>
2) Dirt doesn't work in duels anymore. Its considered a potion and pops you out of the duel. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nirala>Nirala</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>M.C. Hammah</span><br>  Posts: 451<br> <font color=#000000>(6/10/03 8:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=253.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Some undocumented things in 1.62</span><hr size=1> Hmmm, if Dirt is popping you out of a duel (haven't tried it in a duel yet) that's a bug, /appeal it as such. <p>Nirala HammahMastah<br>
&lt;The Kindred&gt;<br>
Gawaine<br>
